{"tid":2253674,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"崩牙駒贊助 冒劉國昌執導 被嫌製作太渣  撐警電影《時代》遭院線割席上映無期","createTime":"2020-10-22T10:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T12:53:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6f8638715d87f4c5076a73bb39e7ee7271e8acd9","tid":2253674,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:14:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201022/O2MWJX7KHZB2PO4SSKGR6NOSAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201022%2FO2MWJX7KHZB2PO4SSKGR6NOSAM%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPaVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=78082759\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201022%2FO2MWJX7KHZB2PO4SSKGR6NOSAM%2F&h=34174f26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201022/O2MWJX7KHZB2PO4SSKGR6NOSAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n崩牙駒贊助 冒劉國昌執導 被嫌製作太渣 <br />\n撐警電影《時代》遭院線割席上映無期<br />\n<br />\n楊明及莊思明等主演的撐警電影《時代》，自開拍以來是非多多，此電影是由崩牙駒大馬公司贊助，和勝和前坐館「沙田Me」翟浩琛投資，再交由其仔女製作。有指電影由劉國昌執導，但他否認，昨日更指因知電影是「深藍」而早就退出。《時代》的預告及海報近日出爐，還被網民狂彈水準極差。電影公司前晚更自行宣佈將於下月在黃百鳴旗下的Cinema City戲院上映，但院商見狀即發聲明澄清，《時代》上映無期。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：王晶拍撐警戲碰壁告吹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lF-SvcKUuq26UmCdE51tWCNSXKU=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VLRXVMXH6VBAHCL2JFF5PGELQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlF-SvcKUuq26UmCdE51tWCNSXKU%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVLRXVMXH6VBAHCL2JFF5PGELQA.jpg&h=88754acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■電影《時代》海報製作粗糙，被網民狂踩連小學生作品都不如。<br />\n<br />\n電影《時代》由「時代電影制作公司」開發與投資，制作公司近日分別在其fb和官網推出預告片及海報，當時有藍絲表明今次是藍黃色電影圈對撼，皆因由《十年》周冠威執導的《幻愛》截至前日在港已有逾1,501萬元票房，藍絲們聲言要力撐《時代》戰勝《幻愛》。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kl3sc4Q-q_DJRAUBuaBjdmvXURo=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X6CI7R4WIFGOTGTDOOHMKL66VQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fkl3sc4Q-q_DJRAUBuaBjdmvXURo%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX6CI7R4WIFGOTGTDOOHMKL66VQ.jpg&h=be009963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《時代》的製作公司前晚自行宣佈電影會在Cinema City上映。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e76n1soZ1hHsGJx3blSfRlv3uHg=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KJRDVRCCJFAPNACHSI6JCGRD5A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe76n1soZ1hHsGJx3blSfRlv3uHg%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKJRDVRCCJFAPNACHSI6JCGRD5A.jpg&h=a40144a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被指偏藍的黃百鳴旗下的Cinema City排片工作由其女兒負責，現拒讓《時代》上映，令黃百鳴處境尷尬。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2QXMl9kRDJ81tcSnrrJbJjp71ME=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FZMFJBGGIVC7DNFZWRUTNGFHR4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2QXMl9kRDJ81tcSnrrJbJjp71ME%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFZMFJBGGIVC7DNFZWRUTNGFHR4.jpg&h=4c33aa3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃百鳴院線急澄清<br />\n<br />\n惟Cinema City昨日凌晨約3時在fb發聲明澄清：「本公司旗下所有戲院並未有為電影《時代》安排任何放映場次。」院方急發聲明後，《時代》fb及網頁昨早即刪除電影在Cinema City上映的資訊。Cinema City院線由近年不時拍合拍片、被指偏藍的黃百鳴創立，據知排片工作由他的女兒負責。不少網民留言贈興：「做乜同藍友割席？」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：預告、海報粗製濫造被狂踩<br />\n<br />\n時代電影制作公司回覆傳媒表示，因題材敏感，受到發行商、戲院等不同政見的阻滯，投資方不惜重金包場戲院，最終找到合適的方法及渠道令電影上映。據知情人士向《蘋果》透露，。。。。。。。。。，以致《時代》現時上映無期。<br />\n<br />\n其實《時代》是由「和勝和」前坐館「沙田Me」翟浩琛投資開拍，並找來他的兒子翟俊威（Aden）執導，但因Aden經驗尚淺，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/U41FZOy6YyRWrC8LKmq9ar5Ikgs=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XZ3FI5GFQJEMPD3KCR3CKF7OYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FU41FZOy6YyRWrC8LKmq9ar5Ikgs%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXZ3FI5GFQJEMPD3KCR3CKF7OYE.jpg&h=e861893a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■無辜被屈做導演的劉國昌，澄清因發現電影是「深藍」而早就退出。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UmievZeHO_UAqNZ4PWHhDDhKHXg=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5U2V34D6KRBILC5PMCNGLSA44A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUmievZeHO_UAqNZ4PWHhDDhKHXg%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5U2V34D6KRBILC5PMCNGLSA44A.jpg&h=9c219f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《時代》導演翟俊威是沙田Me細仔，他還曾經出道做歌手。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yHEc0hMeuwb6A6Zcc-OLyISKvYs=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HNDHFDQ3NFHSVL34OYAQVUBZCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyHEc0hMeuwb6A6Zcc-OLyISKvYs%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHNDHFDQ3NFHSVL34OYAQVUBZCY.jpg&h=ae191002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■崩牙駒的大馬公司有份贊助拍攝《時代》。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇初稿畀少少意見<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》昨日聯絡劉國昌，他表示沒有見過該通告，還笑言寫任何人的名字上去也可以。至於為何被指是導演，劉國昌說：「我識Aden，我啲細姪，開始時佢諗住拍一套電影關於年輕人，冇話藍定黃。後來聽聞投資者包括佢爸爸，因資方問題逼住轉軚，劇本越嚟越藍。我只幫佢睇過初稿，畀咗少少意見，但後來個故事改咗好多，所以我褪軚。因為有好多睇法唔一樣，所以退出。」劉國昌強調無參與拍攝，跟Aden只見過一次。<br />\n<br />\n《時代》製作班底及投資方亦有不同傳聞，先有指是沙田Me為捧紅兒子不惜出錢投資，他跟有份演出的保安局前局長李少光兒子李霖恩也十分老友，有傳是透過李霖恩拉攏才找到現時演員演出。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_8Xk0Ug2-6dfc4GYEc80rbV7LxI=/1280x354/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DETJ4KQA2NCGDOX5LUHEDGFUMM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_8Xk0Ug2-6dfc4GYEc80rbV7LxI%3D%2F1280x354%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDETJ4KQA2NCGDOX5LUHEDGFUMM.jpg&h=06b8e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■網上流出《時代》的開工通告，導演一欄清楚寫上劉國昌、翟俊威。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/33aBQH40QcORuWtWruVXkY_P5lE=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JJC4EQF47RGXTHONQDTWEZ23P4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F33aBQH40QcORuWtWruVXkY_P5lE%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJJC4EQF47RGXTHONQDTWEZ23P4.jpg&h=d25a5cc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《時代》由撐警的楊明、莊思明、曹永廉等主演，沙田Me大仔翟俊朗也有份演出。資料圖片"},{"pid":"cf65f48b2b79aae80375638d3e082affe979c903","tid":2253674,"uid":111316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:16:58.000Z","msg":"放youtube都未必有view<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8437c6b7c819c03e2f32aaa03c6cd0d8cc9688fc","tid":2253674,"uid":182930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"沙田Me點解要戴超戴口罩<br />\n係咪以為冇人認得佢個樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28215bc3a66d8b333a7d54cc9c765ea6ddb541e","tid":2253674,"uid":53672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:18:22.000Z","msg":"張海報影得7過蘋果照妖鏡係點做到到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebb7fd86ce01fb1f1d621e32712541f6a21c725","tid":2253674,"uid":204356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:18:25.000Z","msg":"垃圾屎戲自己圍爐睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed4a1d09c34baee3103de8c89bbd8a1fd4df742","tid":2253674,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:30:17.000Z","msg":"認住呢班幫黑社會拍戲既契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abaeaa5cb41e07e398b055e324e72012b4c59e61","tid":2253674,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"黑社會拍戲得一個原因<br />\n報數洗黑錢"},{"pid":"8f4ff13e2853ab071df9399e199b1afe392bf92b","tid":2253674,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"諗起五毛沙田you"},{"pid":"11b2d01bffbb84dec98aaafa31fdce5d2f23dcc9","tid":2253674,"uid":14125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:34:29.000Z","msg":"油麻they"},{"pid":"7cc9fc3db5bf3a53ac64f3423fc451c290d9c11a","tid":2253674,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"btw原來喬寶寶未走<br />\n之前好似話佢英藉？"},{"pid":"732565b56e486dcb16e9852f09bb8a34450970fe","tid":2253674,"uid":111316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cc9fc3db5bf3a53ac64f3423fc451c290d9c11a","tid":2253674,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"btw原來喬寶寶未走<br />\n之前好似話佢英藉？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"肥到唔撚認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894d1b24b639fcbcbe76e46d7fb5b37d2bb5bdc9","tid":2253674,"uid":138422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"想睇多次幻愛"},{"pid":"9d1d218537049ff8202d299aa3879bb90d91793c","tid":2253674,"uid":56806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"燈光做埋場務<br />\n講究竟製作費落咗幾多隔"}]}